264
00:21:00,059 --> 00:21:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] nad brakom i obitelji.

265
00:21:01,819 --> 00:21:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo 1925.

266
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,599
