269
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:13,200
[SPEAKER_01] I kako da to vratimo natrag?

270
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ima neko koga je Bog odabrao

271
00:21:14,980 --> 00:21:16,839
[SPEAKER_01] da bude najsvetiji i najčišći muž

272
00:21:16,839 --> 00:21:18,579
