[SPEAKER_01] i otac samoga Boga

275
00:21:22,140 --> 00:21:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] a to je Sveti Josip.

276
00:21:23,539 --> 00:21:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad nam nije bio potrebni nego danas.

277
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moram vam priznati

278
00:21:28,140 --> 00:21:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam vidio slike poput

279
00:21:29,859 --> 00:21:31,339
[SPEAKER_01] ove

280
00:21:31,339 --> 00:21:36,240
[SPEAKER_01] nemam baš neki potica reći

281
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] e, ja hoću biti kao on.

282
00:21:37,460 --> 00:21:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam za vas, ali

283
00:21:40,220 --> 00:21:41,420
[SPEAKER_01] meni je ovog.

284
00:21:41,420 --> 00:21:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ovoga

285
00:21:44,279 --> 00:21:47,240
[SPEAKER_01] postoje dva razloga

286
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:49,140
[SPEAKER_01] zbog čega su umjetnici prikazivali

287
00:21:49,140 --> 00:21:50,299
[SPEAKER_01] Svetog Josipa na ovaj način.

288
00:21:50,299 --> 00:21:52,819
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi je zbog apokritnih spisa

289
