[SPEAKER_01] pa se nakon određenog broja godina

297
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] morala nekom dati i oženiti

298
00:22:11,599 --> 00:22:12,660
[SPEAKER_01] pa je ona rekao

299
00:22:12,660 --> 00:22:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] ajde, ok, budem te uzela

300
00:22:14,380 --> 00:22:16,359
[SPEAKER_01] i viš kak sam ja stari, slabi, ovo, ono.

301
00:22:16,359 --> 00:22:18,000
